(2, 1, 'GrOath :The Realm of Modern Networking', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '103.1.100.226', '2024-03-18 10:01:32', '2024-03-18 08:56:07', NULL, NULL, '1710752167.avif', '<p>Growth is the parameter of successful business. Growth in turnover, in assets, in human resources, by number of branches and ultimately, it\'s the number that speaks the actual growth, PAT (Profit after Tax) or in usual terms, net profit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Interestingly, I also see a change in the mindset of the business community now. They also now emphasize if they are growing in creating business connections. Strong connections are directly correlated to the growth of the business. The reasons are multiple. It helps in sourcing correct knowledge, right vendors, apt collaborations, strategic expansion, and the list goes on.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Many of us will agree that right connections make the work getting work done quickly, hassle free, at a better rate and also in a timely manner thus saving cost and energy of the organization.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I term a connection as an asset. A connection made today is at par to creating an asset that can have far reaching benefits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Based on this ideology, I humbly present GrOath, to help you grow your business connections through networking. It is a business networking platform conceptualized to cater to the current need of the business community to create strong business connections.</p>\r\n\r\n<blockquote>GrOath aims to be a catalyst to achieve your Oath to Grow your business.</blockquote>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>3 reasons that explains the creation of GrOath</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>The shrinking world due to technology needs trusted connections. Trust helps to create direct and referral business, and even creates collaborations.</li>\r\n	<li>Being amongst the knowledgeable and thriving business community helps you to stay alert about the current market trends so that you achieve your business goals faster.</li>\r\n	<li>The synergy of the business community helps to generate brand recognition and gives extended support to reach to the wider audience.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p>If this is relatable to you, I invite you to be in the GrOath Community. A community that keeps networking at the crux for your business. It’s a different way to grow your business, but after all you stand out from the world when you make a difference.</p>', 'GrOath : An oath to grow', 'business networking platform in ahmedabad', 'Join the thriving business community  for your business GrOath', '2024-02-18', 'groath-the-realm-of-modern-networking'),
(5, 54, 'Membar Test Blog', NULL, 0, NULL, 1, 0, '103.1.100.226', '2024-03-28 05:41:46', '2024-03-28 05:41:46', NULL, NULL, '1711604506.jpg', '<p>Test Blog description</p>', 'Test Blog Meta Title', 'Test Blog Meta keywoed', 'Test Blog Meta Description', '2024-03-28', NULL),
(17, 88, 'Drive Digital Growth with Our Ecommerce Website Development Company in Ahmedabad', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '182.69.30.199', '2024-05-25 10:36:02', '2024-05-25 10:36:02', NULL, NULL, '1717412626.jpg', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Thinking about selling your products or services online and looking for&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.apolloinfotech.com/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Top E-Commerce Development Company in Ahmedabad</span></a>? In today’s digital age, the internet has become the foundation of modern commerce.Businesses, both large and small, are leveraging the power of the web to reach a global audience and drive growth like never before.But to truly stand out in the online world, you need more than just a presence - you need a top-notch website that captures the attention of your target audience and makes it easy for them to do business with you.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">In this blog post, we\'ll talk about why having a top-notch website is key for your business\'s success. Let\'s get started!</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><h2 style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(33, 37, 41); font-size: 21px; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Ecommerce Website Development Company In Ahmedabad</h2><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">With so many people shopping online these days, having a good website is super important for any business. That\'s where Apollo Infotech comes in! We\'re an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.apolloinfotech.com/ecommerce-website-development\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Ecommerce Website Development Company in Ahmedabad</span></a>&nbsp;and we\'re here to help you build a website that\'ll make your business stand out online. But why is having a great website so important? Well, imagine you have a store. You want it to look nice, right? The same goes for your website! It needs to be easy to use, look good and make it simple for people to buy from you. That\'s where we can help.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">At our Ecommerce Website Development Company in Ahmedabad, we understand the importance of a strong online presence in today’s competitive market. With our expertise and dedication, we empower businesses to succeed. With our team of skilled professionals, we offer a comprehensive range of services tailored to meet the unique needs of each client. From custom website design to cutting-edge ecommerce solutions, we have the tools and expertise to help businesses succeed online.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Here are just a few ways our ecommerce website development company can drive digital growth for your business:</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">1.Tailored Solutions</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">We believe that every business is unique and that’s why we take a personalized approach to website development. Our team works closely with each client to understand their goals, target audience and industry-specific requirements.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Whether you’re a startup looking to establish your online presence or an established brand seeking to revamp your existing website, we have the expertise to bring your vision to life.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;2. User-Centric Design</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">In today’s digital landscape, user experience is most important. A well-designed website not only looks great but also provides a seamless browsing experience for visitors. Our team of designers specializes in creating user-centric designs that are intuitive, responsive and visually appealing. By focusing on usability and accessibility, we ensure that your website engages visitors and encourages them to explore further.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">3. Ecommerce Expertise</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">As the ecommerce market continues to grow, having a robust online store is essential for success. Our ecommerce development team has extensive experience building scalable and secure&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.apolloinfotech.com/blog/top-10-features-of-e-commerce-website\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">ecommerce websites</span></a>&nbsp;that drive sales and maximize revenue. Whether you’re selling physical products, digital downloads, or services, we have the tools and expertise to create a customized ecommerce solution that meets your specific needs.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">4. Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">With millions of websites striving for attention online, standing out from the crowd can be a challenge. That’s where search engine optimization (SEO) comes in. Our SEO experts employ proven strategies to improve your website’s visibility in search engine results and drive organic traffic. From keyword research to on-page optimization, we help you climb the ranks and attract more visitors to your site.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">5. Social Media Integration</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">In today’s social media-driven world, having a strong presence on platforms like Facebook, Instagram and Twitter is essential for reaching and engaging with your target audience. Our ecommerce website development company can integrate social media features into your website, allowing visitors to easily share your content and products with their friends and followers. This not only helps increase brand awareness but also drives traffic back to your website.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">6. Analytics and Reporting</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Understanding how your website is performing is key to driving digital growth. That’s why we provide comprehensive analytics and reporting tools that allow you to track key metrics such as website traffic, user behavior and conversion rates. By analyzing this data, you can identify areas for improvement and make informed decisions to optimize your website for maximum effectiveness.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">7.Ongoing Support and Maintenance</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Building a successful website is an ongoing process. Our ecommerce&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mytebox.com/2024/03/22/7-compelling-reasons-to-choose-a-professional-website-development-company-in-ahmedabad/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">website development company</span></a>&nbsp;offers ongoing support and maintenance services to ensure that your website remains secure, up-to-date and performing at its best. Whether you need technical assistance, security updates or content updates, our team is here to help you every step of the way.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Conclusion</span></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">In conclusion, partnering with our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.apolloinfotech.com/ecommerce-website-development-services\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgba(var(--bs-link-color-rgb),var(--bs-link-opacity,1)); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: bolder; scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">Ecommerce Website Development Company in Ahmedabad</span></a>&nbsp;can help drive digital growth for your business. From professional website design to ecommerce functionality, SEO, social media integration and ongoing support, we provide all the tools and expertise you need to succeed online. So why wait? Contact us today to learn more about how we can help take your digital presence to the next level!</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; text-align: justify; font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); scroll-behavior: smooth !important;\">&nbsp;</p>', 'best IT company in ahmedabad', 'best IT company in ahmedabad<br>', 'best IT company in ahmedabad<br>', '2024-05-25', 'drive-digital-growth-with-our-ecommerce-website-development-company-in-ahmedabad'),
(18, 126, 'RAISING THEM RESILIENT', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '103.249.233.147', '2024-06-17 05:29:34', '2024-06-17 05:29:34', NULL, NULL, '1718602174.jpg', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.25in\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\"><font size=\"4\" style=\"\" face=\"georgia\">The other day, my son and I were building a tower out\r\nof blocks. It was fun to begin with but as the tower soar higher and higher it\r\nbegan to tumble and ultimately collapsed. My son was devastated. Cried and\r\nwhined a lot. Nothing helped to console him. From that incident, he hesitated in\r\nplaying with blocks with the fear that he will fail again in building the\r\ntower. Fear obstructed his way to freedom of thought! Fear of failure, fear of\r\nrejection, fear to commit mistakes, fear of the truth! Similar situations\r\nhappen with us all the time. Children make mistakes, fail often. Sometimes we\r\nencourage them so that they learn from their mistakes. Sometimes we scold them,\r\njudge them. As being a Mother and a Pediatrician, I think teaching them that Failure\r\nis not opposite of Success, it’s a part of it. It’s not how far you fall, but\r\nhow high you bounce back that counts. That is <i style=\"\">Resilience</i>. When resilient\r\nkids step into a situation, they have a sense they can figure out what they\r\nneed to do &amp; with confidence, can handle what is thrown at them. This doesn’t\r\nmean that kids have to do everything on their own. Rather, they know how to ask\r\nfor help &amp; can solve problems step by step.<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.25in\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">Our Culture nowadays, is to make our kids comfortable.\r\nThe idea of putting our children through the same pain as we went through, is just\r\nintolerable. So we, as Parents, try to protect our kids &amp; shield them from\r\nworst case scenarios. Overprotecting children breeds anxiety in them. Instead we\r\ncan help them build resilience through<o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Not accommodating their every need and thus, let the child develop\r\ncapacities of problem solving. With each fall, stop rushing ourselves to\r\ncomfort him unless it’s a grave injury. Children needs an audience to react. So\r\navoid making mountains out of mole, in this case catering to their attention.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Avoid eliminating all risks. Giving age appropriate freedom helps\r\nthem learn their limits. The key is to allow appropriate risks and teach our\r\nchildren essential skills. Practice Supervised Neglect.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Teaching concrete skills. Concrete thinking is reasoning that’s\r\nbased on what you see, hear, feel and experience in the here &amp; now. Its reasoning\r\nthat focuses on physical objects, immediate experiences and exact\r\ninterpretation. It’s basically logical thinking, allowing the child to reason,\r\nknow facts, find solutions. So whenever you need to talk or correct a child,\r\nalways think- where are we going with this situation? What skill do they need\r\nto get?<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Teaching them to solve problems. Engage children in figuring out\r\nhow they can handle challenges. Give them opportunities, over &amp; over, to\r\nfigure out what works and what doesn’t. Help them figure out how to navigate\r\nthe feeling of anxiety and nervousness while learning or trying something new. Brainstorm\r\nideas to overcome that.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Avoid ‘why’ questions. It doesn’t solve problems. Try ‘how’\r\nquestions to fix the problem.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Don’t provide all the answers. Start using ‘I don’t know’ followed\r\nby problem solving. This helps to learn to tolerate uncertainty and think about\r\nways to deal with potential challenges.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Avoid talking in catastrophic terms. Pay attention to what you say\r\nto your children and around them. Anxious parents can bring up anxious\r\nchildren.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">8.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Letting children make mistakes. It helps them to learn to fix slip ups\r\nand make informed decision next time. Don’t expect perfectionism from them.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">9.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Help them manage emotions. Children learn very quickly which\r\npowerful emotions can get them what they want. Parents have to learn how to\r\nride the emotions too. Self-regulation can be taught by being a model ourselves.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%; color: rgb(31, 31, 31);\">10.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp; </span></span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\">Modelling adaptability. Children learn maximum by observing the\r\nparents. When we commit a mistake, admit it and apologize. When we are angry,\r\ntry calming down techniques before talking further.<o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" face=\"georgia\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" style=\"\" face=\"georgia\">Resiliency helps\r\nchildren navigate the inevitable trials, triumphs &amp; tribulations of\r\nchildhood and adolescence. <span style=\"background: white;\">Over time, they\r\nbecome more able to cope with life’s obstacles and hardships, both physically\r\nand mentally.</span> Resilient children become resilient adults and thrive\r\nbetter in the face of life’s unavoidable stressors.</font><span style=\"font-family: Shruti, &quot;sans-serif&quot;; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" style=\"\" face=\"georgia\">Dr. Jil Shah (MD Pediatrics)</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" style=\"\" face=\"georgia\">AROHA Hospitals</font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" style=\"\" face=\"georgia\"><br></font></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 107%;\"><font size=\"4\" style=\"\" face=\"georgia\"><br></font></span></p>', 'How to raise resilience children?<div>How to teach Children to never give up?</div><div>Teaching children into accepting failure.</div><div>Teaching children how to bounce back from failure.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div>', 'failure, children,child,kids,resilience,give up,thrive in stress,fear,mistakes,hardships,acceptance,hope', '<span style=\"font-family: georgia; font-size: large; text-align: justify;\">resiliency helps children navigate the inevitable trials, triumphs &amp; tribulations of childhood and adolescence.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: georgia; font-size: large; text-align: justify; background: white;\">Over time, they become more able to cope with life’s obstacles and hardships, both physically and mentally.</span><span style=\"font-family: georgia; font-size: large; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;Resilient children become resilient adults and thrive better in the face of life’s unavoidable stressors.</span>', '2024-06-17', 'raising-them-resilient');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blogTitle`, `content`, `status`, `rejectedcomments`, `iStatus`, `isDelete`, `strIP`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `blogImage`, `blogDescription`, `metaTitle`, `metaKeyword`, `metaDescription`, `blogDate`, `blog_slug`) VALUES
(19, 126, 'UNPLUG TO CONNECT', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '43.242.116.8', '2024-07-08 04:27:08', '2024-07-08 04:27:08', NULL, NULL, '1720412828.png', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:.25in;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:.25in\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Screen time is the total time spent per\r\nday in viewing screens such as mobile phone, TV, computer, tablet, or any\r\nhand-held or visual device. Screens have become an essential part of our life.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:.25in;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:.25in\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;I, Dr. Jil Shah, as a parent and health\r\nprofessional, am concerned about the increase in children’s screen time. Just\r\nlike the balanced food that we eat, screens need to be properly chosen and to\r\nbe consumed in the right quantity and at the right time. The way we use the\r\nscreens determines whether it is healthy or unhealthy. Screen time spent for\r\neducational or pro social activities such as schoolwork, interacting with\r\nfriends and relatives, and creating art or music or relaxation is termed\r\npositive or healthy, while watching inappropriate TV shows, visiting unsafe\r\nwebsites, or playing violent video games are few examples of negative or\r\nunhealthy screen time. <o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify; margin-left: 0.25in; text-indent: 0.25in;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\">&nbsp;</font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo8\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Children below the age of 2 years should not be\r\nexposed to any type of screen with the exception of occasional video call with\r\nrelatives.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo8\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Screen time for children between the age of 2\r\nand 5 years should not exceed 1 hour; the lesser, the better.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:.75in;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l1 level1 lfo8\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->For older children and adolescents, it is\r\nimportant to balance screen time with other activities that are required for\r\noverall development.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.25in\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">When screens\r\nare used in moderation in a balanced and healthy way, they have many<b><i><span style=\"color:#0070C0\"> benefits</span></i></b>:<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:57.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Encourage learning and knowledge<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:57.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Act as a tool for communicating with friends and\r\nfamily and promote social interaction<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:57.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Healthy co-viewing and co-playing using digital\r\nplatforms improve child and parent bonding, recreation, and relaxation.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:57.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Smartphone Apps such as Calm, and digital\r\nplatforms such as NIMHANS online yoga class encourage kids to adopt healthy\r\nbehaviors and kindle device promotes reading<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:57.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Channels and blogging platforms give\r\nopportunities to children to display their talents<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:57.5pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo6\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Customized computer programs can improve social\r\nbehavior in children with autism and study skills in children with learning\r\nproblems.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:39.5pt;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.5in\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Screen time and\r\ndigital technology have become an inevitable part of childhood, with shift of\r\nlearning and socialization to virtual environments. However, concerns on\r\nill-effects of excessive exposure to screen and digital media have emerged. There\r\nare multiple <b><i><span style=\"color:#0070C0\">ill effects of excessive screen\r\ntime</span></i></b> on child:<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"margin-left:75.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:\r\n77.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><b><i>Physical\r\nhealth:</i></b> Obesity, sedentary lifestyle, disturbed sleep, headache, eye\r\nstrain, neck, back, and wrist pains, postural Kyphosis, poor balance, fatigue,\r\nbody pain resulting from bad posture<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:75.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7;tab-stops:\r\n77.0pt\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]--><b><i>Mental\r\nhealth</i></b>: Delayed speech, hyperactivity, aggression, violence, desire for\r\ninstant gratification, poor concentration, FOMO (fear of missing out), FOBLO\r\n(fear of being left out), cyberbullying, media addiction, distorted perception\r\nof sex by exposure to pornography, drug use, self-harm, anxiety, and depression<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:75.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]--><b><i>Affecting sleep</i></b>: Emitting blue\r\nlight reduces melatonin, creating more alertness and later bedtimes, reduced\r\nsleep hours, insomnia, poor consolidation of memory and learning, daytime\r\ndrowsiness<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:75.5pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]--><b><i>Social</i></b>: Reduced socialization and\r\nsocial anxiety, poor development of expressive language, hampers responsive and\r\ninteractive conversations, affects bonding with family friends, low self esteem\r\nand low confidence<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"margin-left:75.5pt;mso-add-space:auto;\r\ntext-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo7\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]--><b><i>Scholastic</i></b>: Decreased academic\r\nperformance, poor attention and concentration, poor recall, affecting language\r\ndevelopment, affects posture, less time on homework<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.25in\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:.25in\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Children feel\r\nsecure when boundaries and rules are laid down for behavior. You should\r\nformulate “<b><i><span style=\"color:#0070C0\">digital rules</span></i></b>” to\r\nencourage healthy media usage when your child begins to use a digital device.\r\nThese should be age appropriate and new rules could be added as the child\r\nbecomes older. A few rules for maintaining “digital hygiene” are:<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Be\r\na role model about using screen time ourselves<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Create\r\nscreen time <b><i>rules</i></b><o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:112.2pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Discuss with your partner<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:112.2pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Do what works for your family<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:112.2pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Stick to the rules as much as possible<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:112.2pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->A SKING FOR Permission before using<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:112.2pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->When and where to use screens<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->No\r\nscreens during <b><i>meals</i></b><o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:116.35pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Socio-emotional, language, motor development<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:116.35pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->‘No phones at the table’ rule<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:116.35pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Start with avoiding screens or reduce the timing\r\nof screen for single meal, later on with all the mealtimes.<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:116.35pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l4 level1 lfo3\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Offer choices for activities after the meal<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->No\r\nscreens for atleast 1-2 hours before<b><i> bedtime</i></b> so as to wind down\r\nthe brain<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:120.55pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo4\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Turn off notifications so as to avoid constant\r\npings!<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"margin-left:120.55pt;mso-add-space:\r\nauto;text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:l6 level1 lfo4\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">·<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Buy an alarm clock so you don’t have devices in\r\nthe bedrooms<o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l3 level1 lfo1\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><!--[endif]-->Family\r\n<b><i>tech- free days</i></b><o:p></o:p></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left:.25in;text-align:justify\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><b><u><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\">Protecting\r\nfrom the internet<o:p></o:p></font></span></u></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l5 level1 lfo5\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Ensure proper privacy settings on the computer, safe\r\nsearch engines on browsers and apps<b><o:p></o:p></b></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l5 level1 lfo5\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Preview the show before allowing or co-viewing\r\nand monitoring the online content and interactions<b><o:p></o:p></b></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l5 level1 lfo5\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Agree on appropriate length of time they can use\r\ntheir device.<b><o:p></o:p></b></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l5 level1 lfo5\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Offer choices as to when to use or which program\r\nto watch?<b><o:p></o:p></b></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:-.25in;\r\nmso-list:l5 level1 lfo5\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><font size=\"3\" face=\"verdana\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Ø<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal;\">&nbsp;\r\n</span><!--[endif]-->Avoid programs and games with violent content.<b style=\"\"><o:p></o:p></b></font></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><font size=\"5\" style=\"\" face=\"impact\">A SCREEN cannot replace HUMAN\r\nINTERACTION</font><font size=\"3\" style=\"font-family: verdana;\"><o:p></o:p></font></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br></p>', 'SCREEN TIME effects, benefits, adverse effects of screen time', 'screen time, adverse effects of screen time, benefits of screen time, children and screen time, are screens good for kids?, role of screens&nbsp;', 'Screens have become the integral part of our lives. It has both positive and negative effects on children. It can be a great source of education and entertainment. However, excessive screen time can lead to many health problems. Let\'s learn about the effects of screen time, screen discipline rules and how to make the best use of screens in our children\'s lives.', '2024-07-08', 'unplug-to-connect'),
(20, 88, 'SEO Strategies That Work for Ahmedabad Businesses', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '103.1.100.226', '2024-08-02 11:20:07', '2024-08-02 11:20:07', NULL, NULL, '1722597607.jpg', '<div itemprop=\"articleBody\" class=\"entry-content\">\r\n			\r\n<p>For any business owner in Ahmedabad, it is very crucial that the \r\nbusiness is easily found online. An <a href=\"https://www.apolloinfotech.com/seo-company\" title=\"\" target=\"_blank\">SEO service provider in Ahmedabad \r\n</a>can assist you in enhancing your visibility on the search engines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Here are some basic and easy SEO tips that can help your business in Ahmedabad:</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Understanding SEO</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Also referred to as Search Engine Optimization or SEO, is the \r\npractice of optimizing a website in a bid to rank higher on search \r\nengines.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>This means that more and more people will be able to locate your \r\nbusiness when they use the search engine. The best practices in SEO can \r\nassist your enterprise development.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Why SEO Matters for Ahmedabad Businesses</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ahmedabad is an active business hub with many business \r\nestablishments. Being unique in a world can be challenging. That is \r\nwhere SEO comes in. Good SEO ensures that when people in Ahmedabad are \r\nlooking for products or services you offer, they will find you first.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Benefits of Using an SEO Service Provider</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Expert Knowledge:</strong> They are aware of the standards and modern tendencies.</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Time-Saving: </strong>They take care of the SEO as you concentrate on your business.</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li><strong>Better Results:</strong> It is possible to get improved results than if you did it individually.</li></ul>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Expert Knowledge</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>SEO experts know how the search engine works. They monitor changes in\r\n algorithms. This means they can tweak your SEO strategies to ensure \r\nyour site remains high in the ranking.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Time-Saving</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Managing a business is a tiresome task that requires a lot of time. \r\nIt may be overwhelming to include SEO in your list of things to do. An\r\n <a href=\"https://www.apolloinfotech.com/seo-company\"><strong>SEO service provider in Ahmedabad</strong></a> can do this for you.&nbsp; This will make it easier for you to manage your business.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Better Results</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>SEO gurus employ strategies that have been proven effective. They can\r\n tell what your website requires and make adjustments as fast as \r\npossible. You get better results in minimum time.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Key SEO Strategies</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Let’s talk about several important aspects of SEO that may be helpful for your Ahmedabad-based business.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1. Keyword Research</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Search terms are the words that users input into the search engine \r\nbar. It is very important to know and understand the keywords for your \r\nparticular website.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>An SEO expert will identify the correct keywords and phrases best \r\nsuited to your business. This makes customers locate your business.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>2. On-Page SEO</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>On-page SEO deals with the modification of website content. This ensures that visitors get the most from your website.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>This includes using keywords in the title, headings, and the content \r\nof the page or article. This also entails developing good quality \r\ncontent and one that will be of benefit to the visitors.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3. Off-Page SEO</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Off-page SEO means SEO that is done outside of your website or your \r\nown online identity. This could be in the form of getting other websites\r\n to link to your website.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>It also comprises Social Media Marketing and Online Reviews &amp; Ratings.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. Local SEO</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Local SEO is significant for every business and even more crucial for\r\n businesses that are located in Ahmedabad. Most importantly, it assists \r\npeople within your region to identify you.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>This involves claiming the business on Google My Business and getting it to be reviewed by locals.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>5. Mobile Optimization</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>People search on the internet, mostly using their mobile phones. It is important to ensure that your website is responsive.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>This means it can adapt to viewing on a smaller screen such as mobile\r\n phones. A good SEO Service provider Company in Ahmedabad will surely \r\nensure that your site is mobile-friendly.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>6. Regular Updates</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Writing for SEO is not a one-time activity. It is rather a continuous\r\n process that has to be performed constantly. It should be updated \r\nfrequently and must be checked at frequent intervals.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>An SEO service provider company in Ahmedabad will monitor the performance of the website and tinker with it when needed.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>How to go for the Right SEO Service provider Company in Ahmedabad</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>When looking for an SEO service provider in Ahmedabad, it is critical that one gets it right.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>1. Look at their Experience</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Experience matters in SEO. A provider who has been in the business for some time now is likely to have a good reputation.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>It can provide you with quality services that will meet your needs. \r\nGet them to provide samples of their work or other projects they have \r\ndone.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>2. Check their Services</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Ensure the providers offer relevant services. This can combine, for \r\ninstance, keyword research, content development, link acquisition, and \r\nothers.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>3. Read Reviews</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Find out what other customers say about them. Positive customer feedback can make you believe in them.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>4. Ask Questions</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>Feel free to ask questions. Learn how they intend to enhance your SEO and the sort of outcome that you should anticipate.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Conclusion</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>There are many benefits that businesses in Ahmedabad can derive from \r\nSEO. With the help of an experienced SEO service provider in Ahmedabad, \r\nyou can enhance your web presence. This means that customers will be \r\nmany and sales will increase. Hence the expansion of the business.</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<p>An <a href=\"https://www.apolloinfotech.com/\"><strong>SEO service provider company in Ahmedabad</strong></a>\r\n can help you to achieve a lot in your online business. Do not forget to\r\n select a provider who has some experience, offering good services. Your\r\n business has the opportunity to grow with their help.</p>\r\n		</div>', '<pre id=\"line1\"><span><a class=\"attribute-value\">SEO Strategies That Work for Ahmedabad Businesses.</a></span></pre>', 'SEO company in Ahmedabad, best SEO strategy for Ahmedabad business owners, local SEO setup for Ahmedabad business owners<br>', '<pre id=\"line1\"><span><a class=\"attribute-value\">A Leading SEO Service Provider in Ahmedabad can assist you in enhancing your visibility on the search engines.</a></span></pre>', '2024-08-02', 'seo-strategies-that-work-for-ahmedabad-businesses');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blogTitle`, `content`, `status`, `rejectedcomments`, `iStatus`, `isDelete`, `strIP`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `blogImage`, `blogDescription`, `metaTitle`, `metaKeyword`, `metaDescription`, `blogDate`, `blog_slug`) VALUES
(21, 126, 'Shots for Tots: Building Immunity, Busting Myths, and Protecting Our Future!', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '103.240.169.189', '2024-10-30 06:26:15', '2024-10-30 06:26:15', NULL, NULL, '1730269575.png', '<article class=\"w-full text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]\" dir=\"auto\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-7\" data-scroll-anchor=\"false\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><div class=\"m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem]\"><div class=\"group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\"><div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\"><div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\"><div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"d5bdc530-f9df-49ab-b3af-bd4aeaf594cb\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\"><div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\"><p><font size=\"3\">Hello, I’m Dr. Jil Shah from Aroha Hospital, and I’m here to talk about one of the most effective health measures for children—vaccines. Vaccines have transformed child health by preventing diseases that once caused severe illness and even death. In this article, I’ll discuss why vaccines are critical, which ones are essential, and address some common misconceptions that can sometimes cloud the importance of immunization.</font></p><h3><font size=\"3\">1.&nbsp;<i>How Vaccines Protect Health Through Immunity and Herd Immunity</i></font></h3><p><font size=\"3\">Vaccines work by introducing a safe version of a virus or bacteria—like a weakened or inactivated germ—into the body. This allows the immune system to \"learn\" how to recognize and fight the germ without the child actually contracting the disease. This immune memory remains in the body, ensuring that if the child encounters the disease in the future, their immune system can react swiftly and effectively.</font></p><p><font size=\"3\">Beyond protecting the individual, vaccines play a powerful role in what’s called&nbsp;<em>herd immunity</em>. When a large portion of a community is vaccinated, diseases have far fewer opportunities to spread. This indirectly protects those who are most vulnerable—such as newborns, elderly individuals, and those with compromised immune systems—who may not be able to receive certain vaccines themselves. By vaccinating children, we’re not only guarding their health but also contributing to a healthier, safer community for everyone.</font></p><h3><font size=\"3\">2.&nbsp;<i>Essential Vaccines for Children</i></font></h3><p><font size=\"3\">Vaccination schedules are carefully crafted to protect children from diseases at the optimal time. Here’s a list of essential vaccines for children:</font></p><ul><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>BCG</strong>&nbsp;(Bacillus Calmette-Guérin) for tuberculosis: Administered at birth in areas where TB is prevalent, protecting against severe TB infections.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Polio Vaccine</strong>: Polio was once a leading cause of paralysis in children; this vaccine, given as oral drops or injections, prevents it entirely.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Hepatitis B Vaccine</strong>: Given at birth, this protects against hepatitis B, a virus that can cause long-term liver complications.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>DPT</strong>&nbsp;(Diphtheria, Pertussis, Tetanus): This combination vaccine protects against three dangerous bacterial infections—diphtheria, whooping cough, and tetanus.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>MMR</strong>&nbsp;(Measles, Mumps, Rubella): This vaccine protects against three viral infections. Measles can lead to severe complications like pneumonia, while mumps and rubella can also have serious health impacts.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>HIB</strong>&nbsp;(Haemophilus influenzae type b): Prevents infections like meningitis and pneumonia caused by H. influenzae bacteria.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Rotavirus Vaccine</strong>: Rotavirus causes severe diarrhea in infants, often leading to dehydration and hospitalization. This vaccine helps protect against it.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Pneumococcal Vaccine</strong>: Protects against pneumococcal bacteria, which can cause pneumonia, meningitis, and blood infections.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Typhoid Vaccine</strong>: Recommended for children in areas where typhoid fever is common, it prevents this serious bacterial infection that affects the digestive system.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Chickenpox (Varicella) Vaccine</strong>: This vaccine prevents chickenpox, which, while often mild, can lead to complications like bacterial infections of the skin, pneumonia, and encephalitis in some cases.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Hepatitis A Vaccine</strong>: Hepatitis A, a liver infection, is typically spread through contaminated food and water. The vaccine is especially important in areas where the virus is common.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>HPV Vaccine</strong>: Given to pre-teens and teens, the HPV vaccine protects against human papillomavirus, a leading cause of cervical and other cancers.</font></p></li></ul><p><font size=\"3\">Each vaccine is administered at specific ages for maximum effectiveness, helping children develop immunity at crucial stages of growth.</font></p><h3><font size=\"3\">3.&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><i>Dispelling Common Myths about Vaccines</i></span></font></h3><p><font size=\"3\">Despite their benefits, vaccines are sometimes met with skepticism. Let’s debunk a few myths:</font></p><ul><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Myth 1: Vaccines cause autism.</strong>&nbsp;This misconception originated from a now-debunked study, and numerous studies since have shown no link between vaccines and autism. Health organizations like the CDC and WHO have thoroughly confirmed that vaccines are safe and do not cause autism.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Myth 2: Too many vaccines can overwhelm the immune system.</strong>&nbsp;Children encounter numerous pathogens daily; vaccines introduce only a small number of antigens. Their immune systems are well-equipped to handle multiple vaccines at once without becoming overwhelmed.</font></p></li><li><p><font size=\"3\"><strong>Myth 3: Natural immunity is better.</strong>&nbsp;While some believe getting sick naturally provides stronger immunity, it comes at a high risk. Many vaccine-preventable diseases can cause serious complications, hospitalizations, and even death. Vaccines provide safe immunity without exposing children to these risks.</font></p></li></ul><h3><font size=\"3\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><i>The Role of Vaccines in a Healthier Future</i></font></h3><p><font size=\"3\">Vaccines are among the safest, most effective ways to prevent disease and protect children’s health. Thanks to widespread vaccination, diseases like smallpox have been eradicated, and others like polio are nearly eliminated. By following the recommended vaccine schedule, you’re helping give your child the best start in life and contributing to a safer, healthier community.</font></p><p><font size=\"3\">At Aroha Hospital, we’re here to help you make the best health choices for your child. Let’s work together to ensure a brighter, healthier future for them and for everyone around us through vaccination.</font></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class=\"w-full text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]\" dir=\"auto\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-9\" data-scroll-anchor=\"true\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><div class=\"m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem]\"><div class=\"group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\"><div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\"><div class=\"mt-3 w-full empty:hidden\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"mx-auto\"><div class=\"inline-flex rounded-xl border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-700\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center gap-4 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-token-text-secondary\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-5\"><button class=\"text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-md\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M12.1318 2.50389C12.3321 2.15338 12.7235 1.95768 13.124 2.00775L13.5778 2.06447C16.0449 2.37286 17.636 4.83353 16.9048 7.20993L16.354 8.99999H17.0722C19.7097 8.99999 21.6253 11.5079 20.9313 14.0525L19.5677 19.0525C19.0931 20.7927 17.5124 22 15.7086 22H6C4.34315 22 3 20.6568 3 19V12C3 10.3431 4.34315 8.99999 6 8.99999H8C8.25952 8.99999 8.49914 8.86094 8.6279 8.63561L12.1318 2.50389ZM10 20H15.7086C16.6105 20 17.4008 19.3964 17.6381 18.5262L19.0018 13.5262C19.3488 12.2539 18.391 11 17.0722 11H15C14.6827 11 14.3841 10.8494 14.1956 10.5941C14.0071 10.3388 13.9509 10.0092 14.0442 9.70591L14.9932 6.62175C15.3384 5.49984 14.6484 4.34036 13.5319 4.08468L10.3644 9.62789C10.0522 10.1742 9.56691 10.5859 9 10.8098V19C9 19.5523 9.44772 20 10 20ZM7 11V19C7 19.3506 7.06015 19.6872 7.17071 20H6C5.44772 20 5 19.5523 5 19V12C5 11.4477 5.44772 11 6 11H7Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button><button class=\"text-token-text-secondary hover:text-token-text-primary\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-md\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M11.8727 21.4961C11.6725 21.8466 11.2811 22.0423 10.8805 21.9922L10.4267 21.9355C7.95958 21.6271 6.36855 19.1665 7.09975 16.7901L7.65054 15H6.93226C4.29476 15 2.37923 12.4921 3.0732 9.94753L4.43684 4.94753C4.91145 3.20728 6.49209 2 8.29589 2H18.0045C19.6614 2 21.0045 3.34315 21.0045 5V12C21.0045 13.6569 19.6614 15 18.0045 15H16.0045C15.745 15 15.5054 15.1391 15.3766 15.3644L11.8727 21.4961ZM14.0045 4H8.29589C7.39399 4 6.60367 4.60364 6.36637 5.47376L5.00273 10.4738C4.65574 11.746 5.61351 13 6.93226 13H9.00451C9.32185 13 9.62036 13.1506 9.8089 13.4059C9.99743 13.6612 10.0536 13.9908 9.96028 14.2941L9.01131 17.3782C8.6661 18.5002 9.35608 19.6596 10.4726 19.9153L13.6401 14.3721C13.9523 13.8258 14.4376 13.4141 15.0045 13.1902V5C15.0045 4.44772 14.5568 4 14.0045 4ZM17.0045 13V5C17.0045 4.64937 16.9444 4.31278 16.8338 4H18.0045C18.5568 4 19.0045 4.44772 19.0045 5V12C19.0045 12.5523 18.5568 13 18.0045 13H17.0045Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article>', '<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">Why Vaccines Are Essential for Children: Safeguarding Health and Community Well-being</span><br>', 'Vaccination, importance of vaccine, childhood vaccine, myths about vaccination, herd immunity, necessity of vaccines<br>', '<p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">In this article, Dr. Jil Shah from Aroha Hospital explains why vaccines are essential for every child’s health and safety. Vaccines protect not only individual children but also their communities through herd immunity, which reduces the spread of contagious diseases and shields those who can’t be vaccinated. Dr. Shah outlines essential vaccines like BCG, MMR, polio, hepatitis A and B, chickenpox, typhoid, and more, emphasizing how each one plays a role in safeguarding children against serious illnesses.</p><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Additionally, Dr. Shah debunks common vaccine myths—such as the misconception that vaccines cause autism or overload children’s immune systems—offering clarity and reassurance to parents. Vaccines provide safe immunity without the risks of natural infections, making them one of the safest, most effective tools for a healthy future. This article offers an accessible, informative guide to help parents make the best health choices for their children and the wider community.</p>', '2024-10-30', 'shots-for-tots-building-immunity-busting-myths-and-protecting-our-future'),
(22, 126, 'Empowering Parenthood: Nurturing Positive Motivation and Meaningful Connections with Your Child', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '103.249.233.38', '2024-12-04 06:46:27', '2024-12-04 06:46:27', NULL, NULL, '1733294787.jpg', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\"><div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"a01217de-0546-4dbe-8c25-f7c5e08e8bf5\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\"><div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\"><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Parenting is one of the most rewarding yet challenging journey. As parents, we strive to provide the best for our children—not just materially, but emotionally and mentally. One of the most impactful ways we can support our children is by fostering positive motivation, mastering effective communication, and recognizing their efforts. Dr. Jil Shah offers you practical tips to strengthen your bond with your child while equipping them with confidence and resilience.</p><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Understanding Positive Motivation</strong></h3><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Positive motivation is the driving force that encourages children to engage in productive behaviors, achieve their goals, and maintain a hopeful attitude toward challenges. It is built through encouragement, positive reinforcement, and creating an environment where children feel safe and supported. Motivation stems not only from rewards but also from the belief that effort and perseverance can lead to success.</p><h4 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Why Positive Motivation Matters</strong></h4><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><strong>Builds Self-Esteem:</strong>&nbsp;Children who receive encouragement develop a stronger sense of self-worth. They begin to believe in their abilities, which fosters confidence to tackle challenges.</li><li><strong>Encourages Autonomy:</strong>&nbsp;Motivation helps children take ownership of their tasks and goals, making them less reliant on external prompts.</li><li><strong>Promotes Resilience:</strong>&nbsp;When children are motivated, they’re more likely to persevere through setbacks, viewing failures as stepping stones rather than roadblocks.</li></ol><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>How to Foster Positive Motivation</strong></h3><ol><li><b><font color=\"#000000\">In front of your child, talk about their little positive behaviors to your&nbsp;</font></b><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><b>spouse instead of complaints.</b></span></font></li><li style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Celebrate Effort, Not Just Results:</strong>&nbsp;Acknowledge the hard work, dedication, and learning process rather than focusing solely on outcomes.</li><li style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Model Optimism:</strong>&nbsp;Children learn by observing. Displaying a positive attitude toward challenges teaches them to approach problems with a solution-oriented mindset.</li></ol><hr style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>The Art of Communication During Distress</strong></h3><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Children, like adults, experience a range of emotions, and distress is an inevitable part of their growth. The way parents communicate during such times can either soothe or exacerbate their feelings.</p><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Effective communication strengthens trust between parents and children. When children feel heard and understood, they’re more likely to share their thoughts and emotions, fostering a stronger emotional bond.</p><h4 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Strategies for Talking to Kids in Distress</strong></h4><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><strong>Listen Actively:</strong>&nbsp;Give your full attention to your child. Maintain eye contact, nod in acknowledgment, and avoid interrupting. This reassures them that their feelings are valid and important.</li><li><strong>Validate Their Emotions:</strong>&nbsp;Avoid dismissing or minimizing their feelings. Statements like,&nbsp;<em>“I understand this is hard for you”</em>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<em>“It’s okay to feel upset”</em>&nbsp;show empathy.</li><li><strong>Ask Open-Ended Questions:</strong>&nbsp;Instead of asking,&nbsp;<em>“Are you sad?”</em>&nbsp;ask,&nbsp;<em>“Can you tell me what’s bothering you?”</em>This encourages them to express themselves more fully.</li><li><strong>Stay Calm:</strong>&nbsp;Your tone and demeanor set the emotional tone of the conversation. A calm and patient approach helps children feel secure.</li><li><strong>Offer Solutions Together:</strong>&nbsp;Encourage them to think of solutions. For instance,&nbsp;<em>“What do you think we could do to make this better?”</em>&nbsp;This empowers them to problem-solve.</li></ol><hr style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>The Power of Praise</strong></h3><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Praise is a simple yet transformative tool in parenting. Genuine, well-timed praise can reinforce positive behaviors, boost confidence, and strengthen the parent-child relationship.</p><h4 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Why Praising Kids is Beneficial</strong></h4><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><strong>Builds Confidence:</strong>&nbsp;When children hear affirmations, they start to believe in their abilities, which enhances their self-esteem.</li><li><strong>Encourages Repetition of Positive Behaviors:</strong>&nbsp;Praise reinforces behaviors you want to see repeated, like kindness, effort, or perseverance.</li><li><strong>Fosters a Growth Mindset:</strong>&nbsp;Praising effort over innate talent teaches children that abilities can be developed through hard work.</li></ol><h4 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>How to Praise Effectively</strong></h4><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><strong>Be Specific:</strong>&nbsp;Instead of saying,&nbsp;<em>“Good job!”</em>&nbsp;say,&nbsp;<em>“I’m proud of how much effort you put into your homework today.”</em>&nbsp;This highlights the specific action that earned the praise.</li><li><strong>Focus on Effort and Process:</strong>&nbsp;Compliment perseverance, strategy, or improvement. For example,&nbsp;<em>“I love how you kept trying even when the puzzle was tricky.”</em></li><li><strong>Balance Praise and Constructive Feedback:</strong>&nbsp;While praise is vital, it’s also important to provide constructive feedback when necessary. Ensure feedback is framed positively, emphasizing learning and growth.</li></ol><hr style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Supporting Parents: The Foundation of Positive Parenting</strong></h3><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">While much of parenting advice focuses on children, it’s equally crucial to acknowledge the well-being of parents. Parenting is demanding, and to give your best to your child, you need to be emotionally and mentally nurtured.</p><h4 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>Practices for Parental Support</strong></h4><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><strong>Self-Care:</strong>&nbsp;Dedicate time to recharge. Whether it’s a hobby, exercise, or quiet reflection, taking care of yourself enables you to parent more effectively.</li><li><strong>Seek Community Support:</strong>&nbsp;Share your experiences with other parents. Parenting groups or discussions can provide validation, and new ideas.</li><li><b>If still getting confused and helpless- AROHA hospital is always at your service to help you navigate the struggles while enjoying the journey of parenthood.</b></li></ol><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>The Ripple Effect of Positive Parenting</strong></h3><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">When parents adopt positive motivation, empathetic communication, and effective praise, they create a nurturing environment that extends beyond the household. Children raised with these principles are more likely to:</p><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li>Develop healthy self-esteem and emotional intelligence.</li><li>Approach challenges with resilience and creativity.</li><li>Build strong relationships rooted in respect and understanding.</li></ol><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Moreover, positive parenting influences the broader community. Children who grow up feeling valued and motivated often become compassionate, proactive members of society.</p><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Dr Jil Shah is a Paediatric doctor practising at Aroha Hospital , Naranpura, Ahmedabad. She specialises as parenting coach and child psychology. You can access her PodTalk on the link below.&nbsp;https://youtu.be/i4wcjiK8ZHA?si=wGrQV50APs2twFLu&nbsp; Alternatively you can also reach out to her on the contact number ( + 91 8238037160 ).&nbsp;</p><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></p></div></div></div></div>', '<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">Empowering Parenthood: Nurturing Positive Motivation and Meaningful Connections with Your Child</span><br>', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"ed4e8a91-d14e-4226-87b9-3026eae0a21c\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\"><div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\"><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Positive motivation</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Effective communication with children</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Parenting strategies</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Praising children benefits</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Emotional support for kids</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Building child self-esteem</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Growth mindset in parenting</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Talking to kids in distress</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Encouraging resilience in children</span><br><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Strengthening parent-child bond</span><br></div></div></div></div>', '<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Parenting is a dynamic process that requires adaptability, patience, and love. By fostering positive motivation, engaging in empathetic communication, and recognizing your child’s efforts, you provide them with invaluable tools for a fulfilling life. Remember, parenting isn’t about being perfect; it’s about being present, supportive, and willing to grow alongside your child. Together, you and your child can navigate life’s challenges, celebrating the journey every step of the way.</span><br>', '2024-12-04', 'empowering-parenthood-nurturing-positive-motivation-and-meaningful-connections-with-your-child'),
(23, 174, '\"Why Everyone Needs an Annual Health Check-Up: Benefits and Insights\"', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '43.250.158.226', '2024-12-31 06:06:35', '2024-12-31 06:06:35', NULL, NULL, '1735625195.png', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">In today’s fast-paced world, our health often takes a backseat to work, family, and social obligations. However, maintaining good health is the foundation for achieving our goals and enjoying life to its fullest. One of the simplest yet most effective ways to ensure your well-being is by scheduling an annual health check-up. Here’s why it’s a practice everyone should adopt.</p><h3>1.&nbsp;Early Detection Saves Lives</h3><p>Many serious health conditions, such as diabetes, hypertension, and cancer, often develop silently. By the time symptoms appear, the disease may have already progressed. Regular health check-ups can detect these conditions in their early stages, allowing for timely intervention and significantly improving treatment outcomes. Early detection not only saves lives but can also prevent complications and reduce the need for intensive treatments.</p><h3>2.&nbsp;Prevention is Better Than Cure</h3><p>Annual check-ups aren’t just about finding problems; they’re about preventing them. These visits allow healthcare professionals to assess your risk factors for various diseases based on your lifestyle, family history, and current health status. With this information, they can provide personalized advice on diet, exercise, and other lifestyle modifications to keep you healthy.</p><h3>3.&nbsp;Monitor Your Overall Health</h3><p>Even if you feel fine, subtle changes in your body can go unnoticed. Regular check-ups help monitor essential health metrics like blood pressure, cholesterol levels, Blood sugar and weight. Tracking these indicators over time provides valuable insights into your overall health and helps identify trends that may require attention.</p><h3>4.&nbsp;Mental Health Matters</h3><p>Health check-ups aren’t just about physical well-being; they’re an opportunity to discuss mental health too. Stress, anxiety, and depression are common yet often overlooked. A yearly visit gives you a chance to address any mental health concerns with your doctor, ensuring you receive the support you need.</p><h3>5.&nbsp;Save Money in the Long Run</h3><p>While some people may hesitate to invest in annual check-ups due to cost, the reality is that preventive care is far more affordable than treating advanced illnesses. Detecting and managing conditions early can save you from costly medical bills down the line.</p><h3>6.&nbsp;Build a Relationship with Your Healthcare Provider</h3><p>Regular visits to the same healthcare professional help build a trusting relationship. This familiarity ensures your doctor understands your health history, making it easier to provide tailored care and advice.</p><h3>7.&nbsp;Set a Good Example</h3><p>By prioritizing your health, you set a positive example for your family and friends. Encouraging loved ones to take care of their health can create a ripple effect, promoting wellness within your community.</p><h3>What Does an Annual Health Check-Up Include?</h3><p>While the specifics may vary depending on age, gender, and individual health needs, a typical check-up includes:</p><ul data-spread=\"false\"><li><p>Physical examination</p></li><li><p>Blood tests to check cholesterol, sugar levels, liver function , Kidney function and other&nbsp; cancer markers</p></li><li><p>Blood pressure and heart rate monitoring</p></li><li><p>BMI and weight assessment</p></li><li><p>Screening tests based on age and risk factors (e.g., mammograms, Pap smears, colonoscopies)</p></li><li><p>Discussions about lifestyle, mental health, and preventive care</p></li></ul><h3>Take Charge of Your Health Today</h3><p>Life is unpredictable, but taking charge of your health can provide a sense of control and peace of mind. An annual health check-up is a&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">small investment</span>&nbsp;that yields significant returns in the form of<span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">&nbsp;better health, increased longevity,&nbsp;</span>and a<span style=\"font-weight: 600;\">&nbsp;higher quality of life.</span></p><p>At Labix Diagnostics, we’re committed to helping you stay proactive about your health. Our comprehensive health check-up packages are designed to suit your needs and ensure you’re on the right track. Don’t wait for symptoms to appear—schedule your annual health check-up today and take the first step towards a healthier future.</p>', 'The Importance of Annual Health Check-Ups: Why You Should Prioritize Your Well-Being\"', 'Health Check up , screening , Blood test , Body profile , annual Health Check up , Healthy Habbit , Prevention', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">This article is about how Health check up atleast once in a year can save you in a long run</p><p></p>', '2024-12-31', 'why-everyone-needs-an-annual-health-check-up-benefits-and-insights');
INSERT INTO `blogs` (`id`, `user_id`, `blogTitle`, `content`, `status`, `rejectedcomments`, `iStatus`, `isDelete`, `strIP`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `created_by`, `updated_by`, `blogImage`, `blogDescription`, `metaTitle`, `metaKeyword`, `metaDescription`, `blogDate`, `blog_slug`) VALUES
(24, 126, 'Stress in Early Childhood: Causes, Signs, and Prevention Tips for Parents', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '43.242.116.183', '2025-01-01 05:33:53', '2025-01-01 05:33:53', NULL, NULL, '1735709633.jpg', '<article class=\"w-full scroll-mb-[var(--thread-trailing-height,150px)] text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]\" dir=\"auto\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-3\" data-scroll-anchor=\"false\"><div class=\"m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem]\"><div class=\"group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col agent-turn\"><div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\"><div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\"><div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"b1b970ec-7c37-41e2-9f25-2c2cea6b0428\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\"><div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\"><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-weight: var(--vz-body-font-weight);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Yes, preschoolers absolutely experience stress! While it might seem surprising because they don’t face adult responsibilities, their world is full of challenges that can feel overwhelming. For a preschooler, stress is often about navigating new experiences, developing independence, and managing big emotions they don’t yet understand or know how to express.</font></span></h3><h3><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"3\"><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">As a </span></font><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Pediatrician</span><font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">&nbsp;and Parenting Coach, Dr. Jil Shah has been addressing concerns by the parents and helping them understand and manage their little ones\' big emotions.</span></font></font></h3><div><font face=\"comic sans ms\"><font color=\"#000000\" size=\"5\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><br></span></font></font></div><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"5\" color=\"#ff0000\">Signs of Stress in Preschoolers</font></h3><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Stress in preschoolers can sometimes be mistaken for regular mood swings, but here are some signs to watch for:</font></p><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Behavioral Changes</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;A usually outgoing child suddenly becomes clingy, refusing to play with others or attend school.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it happens:</strong>&nbsp;They may be worried about separation or a new environment.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Sleep Issues</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Your child, who normally sleeps well, starts waking up at night due to nightmares or struggles to fall asleep.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it happens:</strong>&nbsp;Stress can make them feel unsafe, even in their dreams.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Physical Complaints</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Complaining of tummy aches or headaches before school or playdates.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it happens:</strong>&nbsp;Children can express emotional discomfort through physical symptoms.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Regression</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;A preschooler who was toilet-trained starts wetting the bed again.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it happens:</strong>&nbsp;Stress can disrupt their sense of control.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Mood Swings</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Your calm child suddenly has frequent tantrums or meltdowns over small things.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it happens:</strong>&nbsp;They may feel overwhelmed and lack the words to explain their feelings.</font></li></ul></li></ol><hr style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"5\" color=\"#0033cc\">Common Causes of Stress in Preschoolers</font></h3><ul style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Changes in Routine</strong>: Starting school, moving houses, or a new sibling can feel overwhelming.</font><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;“Why can’t I stay home with mommy anymore?”</font></li></ul></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Parental Stress</strong>: Children often pick up on and mirror the stress of their caregivers.</font><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;If parents argue about finances, kids may become anxious without knowing why.</font></li></ul></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Fear of the Unknown</strong>: Monsters under the bed, loud thunderstorms, or meeting new people can feel frightening.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Over-Scheduling</strong>: Too many activities without downtime can overwhelm their little minds.</font></li></ul><hr style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"5\" color=\"#009933\">Handling Stress in Preschoolers</font></h3><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Talk and Listen</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;If they say, “I don’t want to go to school,” respond with, “Can you tell me what you feel when you think about school?”</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it works:</strong>&nbsp;It helps them feel heard and validated.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Create a Safe Space</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Set up a “calm corner” with their favorite books, stuffed toys, and soft blankets.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it works:</strong>&nbsp;It gives them a physical place to decompress.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Maintain Predictability</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Stick to a morning and bedtime routine, even during holidays.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it works:</strong>&nbsp;Routine makes them feel secure.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Teach Simple Relaxation Techniques</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Guide them to take deep breaths like “smelling a flower and blowing out a candle.”</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it works:</strong>&nbsp;It’s a fun, easy way to reduce anxiety.</font></li></ul></li></ol><hr style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"5\" color=\"#ff6600\">Preventing Stress in Preschoolers</font></h3><ol style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Quality Time Together</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Have “pajama picnics” or storytelling sessions before bed.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it works:</strong>&nbsp;It builds trust and strengthens your bond.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Encourage Playtime</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Let them play freely with blocks or in the park without interference.</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it works:</strong>&nbsp;Play helps them process emotions and develop coping skills.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Set Realistic Expectations</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;Avoid saying, “You must win the race,” and instead encourage, “Let’s have fun running!”</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it works:</strong>&nbsp;It reduces pressure and focuses on joy.</font></li></ul></li><li><p><strong><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Monitor Your Stress</font></strong></p><ul><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;If you’re juggling deadlines, explain in simple terms: “Mommy is busy today, but we’ll play together after dinner.”</font></li><li><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><strong>Why it works:</strong>&nbsp;It shows them you’re in control of your stress, too.</font></li></ul></li></ol><hr style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><h3 style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"5\" color=\"#990099\">Real-Life Parenting Tip: “Big Feelings Basket”</font></h3><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Whenever your child feels upset, offer them a “Big Feelings Basket” filled with crayons, paper, squishy toys, and their favorite snacks. Encourage them to draw, squeeze, or even just hug their favorite teddy to let out their emotions.</font></p><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">Remember, stress in kids isn’t always bad—it helps them learn resilience when guided with love and patience. Let them know you’re their safe harbor, always.&nbsp;</font></p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-2 flex gap-3 empty:hidden -ml-2\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><div class=\"items-center justify-start rounded-xl p-1 z-10 -mt-1 bg-token-main-surface-primary screen-arch:mt-1 md:absolute md:sr-only\"><div class=\"flex items-center\"><span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><button type=\"button\" id=\"radix-:rdr:\" aria-haspopup=\"menu\" aria-expanded=\"false\" data-state=\"closed\" class=\"cursor-pointer h-[30px] rounded-md px-1 text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-main-surface-secondary\"><div class=\"flex items-center pb-0\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" class=\"icon-sm\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5.29289 9.29289C5.68342 8.90237 6.31658 8.90237 6.70711 9.29289L12 14.5858L17.2929 9.29289C17.6834 8.90237 18.3166 8.90237 18.7071 9.29289C19.0976 9.68342 19.0976 10.3166 18.7071 10.7071L12.7071 16.7071C12.5196 16.8946 12.2652 17 12 17C11.7348 17 11.4804 16.8946 11.2929 16.7071L5.29289 10.7071C4.90237 10.3166 4.90237 9.68342 5.29289 9.29289Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path></font></svg></div></button></span></div></div></div><div class=\"pr-2 lg:pr-0\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"></div></div></div></div></div></article><article class=\"w-full scroll-mb-[var(--thread-trailing-height,150px)] text-token-text-primary focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-[-4px]\" dir=\"auto\" data-testid=\"conversation-turn-4\" data-scroll-anchor=\"false\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><h5 class=\"sr-only\"><font face=\"comic sans ms\" size=\"4\">You said:</font></h5><div class=\"m-auto text-base py-[18px] px-3 md:px-4 w-full md:px-5 lg:px-4 xl:px-5\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex flex-1 gap-4 text-base md:gap-5 lg:gap-6 md:max-w-3xl lg:max-w-[40rem] xl:max-w-[48rem]\"><div class=\"group/conversation-turn relative flex w-full min-w-0 flex-col\"><div class=\"flex-col gap-1 md:gap-3\"><div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\"><div data-message-author-role=\"user\" data-message-id=\"aaa296ad-e65b-4e79-b02e-fdc3c7ee373c\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden items-end rtl:items-start\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></article>', '<span style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">Stress in Early Childhood: Causes, Signs, and Prevention Tips for Parents</span><br>', '<strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Preschooler stress signs,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Stress in young children,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Causes of stress in preschoolers,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Handling stress in kids,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Childhood stress management,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Behavioral changes in preschoolers,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Emotional regulation in toddlers,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Separation anxiety in preschoolers,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Helping kids cope with stress,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Stress prevention in early childhood,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Parental impact on child stress,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Managing preschool anxiety,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Developmental stress in children,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Stress symptoms in toddlers,&nbsp;</strong><strong style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">How to calm a stressed child</strong><br>', '<div class=\"flex max-w-full flex-col flex-grow\" style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><div data-message-author-role=\"assistant\" data-message-id=\"f7441d0f-5bab-40d4-ac6d-f47ccac1dbe3\" dir=\"auto\" class=\"min-h-8 text-message flex w-full flex-col items-end gap-2 whitespace-normal break-words text-start [.text-message+&amp;]:mt-5\" data-message-model-slug=\"gpt-4o\"><div class=\"flex w-full flex-col gap-1 empty:hidden first:pt-[3px]\"><div class=\"markdown prose w-full break-words dark:prose-invert light\"><h3>Common Reasons Preschoolers Feel Stressed:</h3><ol><li><strong>Separation Anxiety</strong>: Saying goodbye to parents at school or daycare.<ul><li><em>Example:</em>&nbsp;“Why is mommy leaving me here?”</li></ul></li><li><strong>New Situations</strong>: Starting preschool, moving homes, or meeting new people.</li><li><strong>Overstimulation</strong>: Loud noises, crowded places, or a packed schedule.</li><li><strong>Desire for Control</strong>: They may feel frustrated when they can\'t choose or do something independently.</li><li><strong>Parental Stress</strong>: They pick up on the emotions of caregivers and may mirror that stress.</li></ol><h3>What Stress Looks Like in Preschoolers:</h3><ul><li>Crying or tantrums over small things.</li><li>Clinginess or withdrawing from activities they usually enjoy.</li><li>Trouble sleeping, changes in appetite, or physical complaints like stomachaches.</li></ul><p>While stress is normal and even helps children develop coping skills, it’s important to recognize the signs and offer support to help them feel secure and confident in managing their emotions.</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 1.53125rem; font-weight: 600; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Quick Tip to Handle Stress in Preschoolers ?</span></p></div></div></div></div><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><strong>\"Name it to Tame it\"</strong></p><ul style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><li><strong>What to Do:</strong>&nbsp;When your child seems upset or overwhelmed, help them label their feelings. Say, “Are you feeling worried because I’m leaving for work?”</li><li><strong>Why it Works:</strong>&nbsp;Naming emotions makes them less scary and helps kids feel understood.</li><li><strong>Bonus Tip:</strong>&nbsp;Offer a solution like a hug or a calming activity (e.g., coloring, deep breathing).</li></ul><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">?&nbsp;<strong>Example:</strong>&nbsp;“Let’s take three big breaths together and then draw a picture of what’s on your mind!”</p><p style=\"caret-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">It’s simple, quick, and connects you to your child emotionally.</p>', '2025-01-01', 'stress-in-early-childhood-causes-signs-and-prevention-tips-for-parents'),
(25, 174, 'Alarming Rise of Diabetes in India: A Growing Health Concern', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '103.250.137.47', '2025-01-03 08:59:32', '2025-01-03 08:59:32', NULL, NULL, '1735894772.png', '<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">India, often referred to as the diabetes capital of the world, is witnessing an alarming rise in the prevalence of diabetes. With over 77 million people diagnosed as diabetic and many more at risk, this condition has become a pressing health concern. The rapid urbanization, sedentary lifestyles, unhealthy eating habits, and genetic predisposition have contributed significantly to this surge. Understanding diabetes, its implications, and the role of early diagnosis and preventive measures is critical to combating this epidemic.</p><div><hr></div><h4>What is Diabetes?</h4><p>Diabetes is a chronic condition characterized by high blood sugar levels resulting from the body\'s inability to produce or effectively use insulin. The two main types are:</p><ol data-spread=\"false\" start=\"1\"><li><p><strong>Type 1 Diabetes:</strong> An autoimmune condition where the pancreas produces little or no insulin.</p></li><li><p><strong>Type 2 Diabetes:</strong> A more common form associated with insulin resistance and often linked to lifestyle factors.</p></li></ol><p>Other forms include gestational diabetes, which occurs during pregnancy, and prediabetes, a state where blood sugar levels are higher than normal but not yet diabetic.</p><div><hr></div><h4>The Growing Diabetes Epidemic in India</h4><p>India’s diabetes burden is growing due to:</p><ol data-spread=\"false\" start=\"1\"><li><p><strong>Urbanization:</strong> Rapid urban growth has led to lifestyle changes, including reduced physical activity and increased consumption of processed foods.</p></li><li><p><strong>Obesity:</strong> Rising obesity rates, especially among urban populations, are a major risk factor.</p></li><li><p><strong>Genetics:</strong> Indians have a higher genetic predisposition to diabetes compared to other populations.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lack of Awareness:</strong> Many people remain undiagnosed or receive delayed treatment due to insufficient knowledge about the disease.</p></li></ol><p>The consequences of unmanaged diabetes are severe and include complications like<b> heart disease</b>,<b> kidney failure</b>, <b>vision problems</b>, and<b> nerve damage.</b></p><div><hr></div><h4>Role of Pathology in Diabetes Management</h4><p>Pathology plays a pivotal role in managing diabetes effectively. Through advanced diagnostic tools and regular monitoring, pathology laboratories help patients and healthcare providers stay ahead of the disease. Key diagnostic tests include:</p><ol data-spread=\"false\" start=\"1\"><li><p><strong>Fasting Blood Sugar (FBS):</strong> Measures blood sugar levels after an overnight fast.</p></li><li><p><strong>Postprandial Blood Sugar (PPBS):</strong> Assesses sugar levels after a meal.</p></li><li><p><strong>HbA1c Test:</strong> Provides a three-month average of blood sugar levels, helping in long-term management.</p></li><li><p><strong>Lipid Profile:</strong> Checks for cholesterol and triglyceride levels, often altered in diabetics.</p></li><li><p><strong>Kidney Function Tests:</strong> Essential for monitoring diabetic nephropathy.</p></li></ol><p>Early detection through these tests can significantly improve outcomes by enabling timely interventions.</p><div><hr></div><h4>Preventive Measures to Combat Diabetes</h4><p>While the rise in diabetes is concerning, it is preventable and manageable with the right measures:</p><ol data-spread=\"false\" start=\"1\"><li><p><strong>Healthy Eating:</strong> Incorporate a balanced diet rich in whole grains, lean proteins, fruits, and vegetables while avoiding excessive sugar and processed foods.</p></li><li><p><strong>Regular Exercise:</strong> Engage in at least 30 minutes of moderate physical activity daily to maintain a healthy weight.</p></li><li><p><strong>Routine Screening:</strong> Regular check-ups, especially for those with a family history of diabetes.</p></li><li><p><strong>Stress Management:</strong> Practice mindfulness and stress-reducing activities like yoga or meditation.</p></li><li><p><strong>Avoid Smoking and Alcohol:</strong> These can exacerbate diabetes-related complications.</p></li></ol><div><hr></div><h4>The Way Forward</h4><p>Addressing the diabetes epidemic in India requires a multi-faceted approach, including public health initiatives, awareness campaigns, and accessible healthcare services. <b>Pathology labs </b>play an indispensable role in this fight by providing accurate diagnostics and facilitating continuous monitoring.</p><p>At Labix Diagnostics, we are committed to empowering individuals with early detection and comprehensive care. Together, we can curb the rise of diabetes and create a healthier future for India.</p><p>&nbsp;Prioritize your health today—get tested, stay informed, and adopt a healthier lifestyle.</p><p>Myself Dr Prexa Shah - pathologist at Labix DIagnostics , provide all Pathology related services pan ahmedabad. call 9726676762 to get yourself tested.</p><p></p>', '<h3 data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Alarming Rise of Diabetes in India: A Growing Health Concern &amp; covering its causes, pathology\'s role, and preventive measures.</h3>', 'DIABETES , GROWING HEALTH CONCERN , DIABETES CAPITAL-INDIA , SUGAR , BLOOD SUGAR , BLOOD TEST , PATHOLOGY LABORATORY', 'This article is about how diabetes is growing in India and we even dont know its cause. How to prevent it &amp; Manage it by taking very small steps.', '2025-01-03', 'alarming-rise-of-diabetes-in-india-a-growing-health-concern'),
(26, 150, 'Empathy - A Two Way Street', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 0, '157.32.65.186', '2025-01-24 17:58:40', '2025-01-24 17:58:40', NULL, NULL, '1737741520.png', '<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><b>In recent weeks</b>, the conversation about long working hours and personal time has reignited a vital discussion about work-life</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">balance. But in the midst of these debates, one group of individuals often goes unnoticed—<b>caregivers, nannies, and elder</b></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><b>companions.</b></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">These individuals are the silent backbone of many families. They work tirelessly, often 24/7, to ensure patients, elders, and</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">children are cared for with empathy and dedication. Yet, their contributions are undervalued, and their rights often ignored.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><br></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">As the founder of <b>Neev Home HealthCare,</b> I’ve seen this struggle up close. Even when we ensure caregivers receive their due</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">rest and leave, families and guardians often resist:</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><br></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><ul><li><i><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">“What are they here for?”</span><br></i></li><li><i><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">“We’re paying them for this, aren’t we?”</span><br></i></li><li><i><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">“We provide food and shelter—shouldn’t that be enough?”</span><br></i></li></ul></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><b>This mindset fails to recognize a fundamental truth:</b></font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><b><br></b></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">Caregivers are the reason families can balance work and personal life. They bear the stress and responsibility of caregiving,</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">allowing others to work peacefully and spend quality time with loved ones.</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">And yet, when caregivers ask for rest, they are refused, criticized, or even denied pay.</font></p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><br></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><b>Why This Needs to Change</b></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">Empathy is a two-way street. Those who care for us deserve the same respect and humanity in return. As a society, we need</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">to:</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><ol><li><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Respect their time and provide them with regular breaks.</span><br></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Value their work for the emotional and physical effort it demands.</span><br></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Treat them with dignity—they are not just “helpers,” but humans with needs and rights.</span><br></li></ol></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><b>A Call to Action</b></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">Let’s reflect on how we treat those who dedicate their lives to caring for others. It’s time to:</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><ul><li><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Recognize their sacrifices.</span><br></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Support their right to rest.</span><br></li><li><span style=\"font-family: arial; font-size: small; text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Ensure their contributions are acknowledged and appreciated.</span><br></li></ul></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\">Because without caregivers, life as we know it would come to a standstill. <b>Let’s give back the empathy they offer us every</b></font></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-feature-settings: normal; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-variation-settings: normal; color: rgb(53, 53, 53);\"><font size=\"2\" face=\"arial\"><b>day.</b></font></p>', '<br>', '&nbsp;home healthcare , empathy, Neev, compassion, eldercare, workalifebalance, caregiver, homecare,', '<br>', '2025-01-24', 'empathy-a-two-way-street');
