(26, 61, 'Name Plate', '1715329169.png', 'An MDF tray with coasters to gift to your clients and associates this festive season.&nbsp;', 400, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '182.69.30.199', 121, NULL, '2024-05-10 08:19:29', NULL, 'fixed', NULL),
(51, 44, 'personalized mug', '1717472812.jpeg', 'birtday gift', 120, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '182.69.30.199', 104, NULL, '2024-06-04 03:46:52', NULL, 'fixed', 'mug, persolized mug, return gift'),
(52, 66, 'Vaccination', '1717584633.jpeg', '<div>A vaccine is a substance that helps your body build immunity to a particular disease. It\'s usually made from a weakened or dead version of the virus or bacteria that causes the disease. When you get vaccinated, your body learns how to fight off the disease without actually getting sick.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Vaccines are one of the most effective ways to prevent the spread of infectious diseases. They protect not only you but also those around you who may be more vulnerable to the disease, like young children, elderly people, and those with weakened immune systems. When enough people in a community are vaccinated, it creates herd immunity, which means the disease has a harder time spreading from person to person.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div>', NULL, 500, 4500, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.166.91', 126, NULL, '2024-06-05 10:50:33', NULL, 'ranged', 'Birth vaccine, painless vaccine, cervical cancer vaccine, flu vaccine, pneumococcal vaccine, rotavirus vaccine, chicken pox vaccine, typhoid vaccine, hepatitis A vaccine'),
(53, 66, 'Parental counselling', '1717585134.jpeg', 'There is no one-size-fits-all approach to parenting. Every child is different, and every parent is different. However, there are some techniques that have been proven to be effective across the board.<br><div>Some of the techniques are positive reinforcement, setting clear boundaries and expectations, consistent with your style, having patience, perseverance and your presence.</div><div>Learning as we grow is the key to mindful parenting.</div>', 1000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.166.91', 126, 126, '2024-06-05 10:56:02', '2024-06-05 10:58:54', 'fixed', 'Child behaviour, remedies for hitting, mindful parenting, word exercises'),
(54, 66, 'General checkup', '1717585437.jpeg', '<div>As a parent, it can be really scary when your child gets sick, but it\'s important to know what to look out for and when to seek medical attention.</div><div><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;\">Some&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">common childhood illnesses include things like the common cold, ear infections, and stomach bugs. While they can be uncomfortable for your child, they typically aren\'t serious and can be treated at home with rest, fluids, and over-the-counter medication.</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>However, there are some signs that your child\'s illness may require medical attentio and a need for a doctor.&nbsp;</div>', NULL, 400, 700, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.166.91', 126, 126, '2024-06-05 11:01:32', '2024-06-05 11:03:57', 'ranged', 'Infections, sick child, fever, not feeling well, ill kid'),
(55, 66, 'Indoor admission services', '1717585830.jpeg', '<div>Severe sickness in children can be caused by a variety of factors such as infections, chronic illnesses, or even trauma. Some common symptoms of severe sickness in children are high fever, difficulty breathing, dehydration, and severe pain.</div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align); -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;\">It is important to admit children with severe sickness to the hospital as they have the resources and expertise to properly diagnose and treat these conditions. They have access to advanced medical equipment and trained professionals who can monitor the child\'s condition around the clock.</span><br></div><div><br></div><div>Admitting a child to the hospital can be a scary and stressful experience for both the child and their family. However, it\'s important to remember that seeking medical attention early on can prevent the condition from worsening and potentially save a child\'s life.</div><div><br></div><div>If you suspect that your child is experiencing severe sickness, don\'t hesitate to seek medical attention at AROHA Hospital. AROHA provides the best holistic health care solutions to your munchkins in a kids friendly atmosphere and with the highly trained professional staff.&nbsp;</div>', NULL, 3500, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.163.4', 126, NULL, '2024-06-05 11:10:30', NULL, 'ranged', 'Very sick child, monitoring of child, not taking orally'),
(56, 66, 'Child development assessment', '1717586485.jpeg', '<div>Child development is the process by which children grow and learn new skills, both physical and mental. From crawling to walking, babbling to talking, and everything in between.</div><div><br></div><div>Monitoring the development can help identify any potential issues early on. For example, if a child isn\'t meeting certain milestones like sitting up or making eye contact by a certain age, it could be a sign of a developmental delay or disorder.</div><div><br></div><div>By catching these issues early, we can intervene and provide the necessary support and interventions to help the child reach their full potential. This could include things like therapy, specialized education programs, or medical treatments.</div><div><br></div><div>Additionally, monitoring a child\'s development can help us understand their unique strengths and weaknesses. This information can be used to tailor their education and activities to best suit their needs and interests.</div><div><br></div><div>Regular check-ups with us are a great place to start. They can track your child\'s growth and development over time and identify any concerns.</div><div><br></div><div>And don\'t forget to pay attention to your child\'s behavior and interactions with others. Are they making eye contact? Responding to their name? Playing with toys appropriately?</div><div><br></div>', NULL, 700, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.163.4', 126, NULL, '2024-06-05 11:21:25', NULL, 'ranged', 'Autism, ADHD, Cerebral palsy, LD, atypical behaviour, sensory difficulties'),
(58, 43, 'Routine Eye Check up', '1717679397.jpeg', 'Routine Eye check up includes details of every parameter of eye along with eye power check up.', NULL, 700, 2500, NULL, 1, 0, '122.161.189.191', 103, NULL, '2024-06-06 13:09:57', NULL, 'ranged', 'Eye power test, Refraction test, Eye pressure check up, Retinal evaluation'),
(59, 43, 'Cataract surgery', '1717679710.jpg', 'Shine Aesthetic and eye clinic is equipped with most advanced machines for cataract surgeries. Dr. Shwetambari Singh has performed more than 10000 cataract surgeries. She has expertise in implanting various types of premium intraocular lenses like, Toric lenses, Multifocal lenses, Trifocal lenses, EDOF lenses etc.&nbsp;<div>She has trained more than 100 ophthalmologists for performing various eye surgeries.</div>', NULL, 25000, 120000, NULL, 1, 0, '122.161.189.191', 103, NULL, '2024-06-06 13:15:10', NULL, 'ranged', 'Cataract surgery, IOL surgery, Premium lens surgery, Intraocular lens surgery'),
