(76, 42, 'Plain copper bottles', '1718182348.jpg', 'Remind yourself to stay hydrated aesthetically with Pure Copper bottles from SWASTIK COPPER.\r\nWe design bottles that please your eyes, enrich your health with the goodness of copper &amp; come in three different sizes. Ready to beat the summer with the health benefits of Copper?', NULL, 600, 800, NULL, 1, 0, '183.83.147.51', 102, 102, '2024-06-12 08:52:28', '2024-06-14 10:03:38', 'ranged', '#swastkcopper #copperbottle #copperproducts #handmade #auspicious #history #metal #pratikcopper #health #wellness #hollistic #wellbeing #healthylifestyle #culture #india'),
(78, 42, 'Printed copper bottles', '1718184248.jpg', '<div>Remind yourself to stay hydrated aesthetically with Pure Copper bottles from SWASTIK COPPER.</div><div><br></div><div>We design bottles that please your eyes, enrich your health with the goodness of copper &amp; come in three different sizes and prints.\r\nIKKAT PRINTS\r\nMARBLE PRINTS', NULL, 650, 850, NULL, 1, 0, '183.83.147.51', 102, 102, '2024-06-12 09:24:08', '2024-06-14 10:01:25', 'ranged', '#swastkcopper #copperbottle #copperproducts #handmade #auspicious #history #metal #pratikcopper #health #wellness #hollistic #wellbeing #healthylifestyle #culture #india #madeinindia #indianhistory #indianculture #wellnessproducts #tradition #innovation'),
