(83, 63, 'Warrior Queen Process', '1718692840.jpg', '<p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Awaken your power with the Warrior Queen Program</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Are you ready to break free from limitations and Awaken your inner power?&nbsp;</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">The Warrior Queen Program is here to guide you on a transformative journey to achieve your Top 10 goals for the year, empowering you to thrive in your career and personal life.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Introduction:</strong>&nbsp;Our Warrior Queen Program is designed specifically for women who feel stuck in their careers or are aspiring housewives yearning to start something new but are held back by doubts, fears, or limiting beliefs. We believe that every woman has the potential to be a queen in her own life, and our mission is to help you discover and harness that power.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Discover the 3 Secrets to Your Success:</strong></p><ol style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><strong>Uncover Hidden Obstacles:</strong>&nbsp;We\'ll help you identify and eliminate the \'leakages\'—negative thoughts, limiting beliefs, fears, and doubts that are holding you back. By addressing these blind spots, you can move forward with confidence and clarity.</p></li><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><strong>Learn from Your Past:</strong>&nbsp;Our program guides you in creating personalized guidelines based on your past accomplishments and disappointments. This helps you avoid repeating mistakes and leverage your strengths for future success.</p></li><li style=\"margin-left: 15px;\"><p><strong>Define Your Roles and Goals:</strong>&nbsp;We assist you in identifying your various life roles and setting meaningful goals for each. This comprehensive approach ensures that you are not only achieving career success but also thriving in your personal life.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p></li></ol><div>We Purvi &amp; Pritesh have a mission to create an army of 1,00,000 women who wants to design their Destiny. If you are one of them then do enroll in our Warrior Queen Program and Transform your Life! For more details do check our website&nbsp;https://www.pritesh-shah.com/warriorqueen</div>', NULL, 5000, 8000, NULL, 1, 0, '49.43.32.48', 123, 123, '2024-06-18 06:40:40', '2024-07-10 11:11:52', 'ranged', '#transformation #coaching #training #womencoaching #growth #hilisticgrowth #blindspots #chenginglives #purvipritesh #purvishah #priteshshah #purvipriteshconsultancy #successabundancecoach'),
(84, 63, 'Home Meeting Mastery Blue Print', '1718693402.jpg', '<h3 style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Ultimate Guide to Profitable Home Meetings</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Are you ready to transform your home into a powerhouse for business success?</strong></p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">Welcome to the \"Ultimate Guide to Profitable Home Meetings,\" your all-in-one resource designed to help network marketers, insurance agents, and beauty professionals turn home meetings into high-conversion opportunities.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>About the Program:</strong>&nbsp;In today’s competitive market, personal connections are more valuable than ever. Our program provides you with the tools and strategies to leverage these connections for maximum business impact. Here’s what you’ll discover:</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Secret #1: Monetizing Personal Connections</strong>&nbsp;Unlock the potential within your existing network. Learn how to turn casual acquaintances into meaningful business relationships that drive sales and growth.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Secret #2: Overcoming Presentation Anxiety</strong>&nbsp;Say goodbye to nerves and hello to confidence. Our program equips you with techniques to manage and overcome presentation anxiety, ensuring you deliver engaging and persuasive meetings every time.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Secret #3: The Framework for Inviting, Leading, and Closing</strong>&nbsp;Success starts with a solid plan. Discover our proven framework that guides you through the entire process of hosting home meetings—from sending out compelling invitations to leading dynamic presentations and closing sales effectively.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Why Home Meetings?</strong>&nbsp;Home meetings are cost-effective, create a comfortable environment for decision-making, and allow for a more personal touch. They lead to higher engagement, stronger relationships, and increased conversion rates compared to traditional methods.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\"><strong>Ready to Skyrocket Your Business?</strong>&nbsp;Don’t miss out on this opportunity to elevate your business. Join our program today and start hosting home meetings that not only connect but convert.</p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">.For more details please check our website -&nbsp;https://homemeeting.pritesh-shah.com/</p>', NULL, 15000, 25000, NULL, 1, 0, '49.36.89.115', 123, NULL, '2024-06-18 06:50:02', NULL, 'ranged', '#homemeeting #sales #recruitment #networkmarketer #insuranceagent #blueprint #masteringthemeeting #purvipriteshconsultancy #transformation #growth #coaching #successabundancestrategists'),
(87, 42, 'Copper Kalash (Gadwa)', '1719313758.jpg', '<div>Shreerang Copper Kalash is crafted from pure copper to enhance your festive rituals. This sacred vessel embodies divine energy and blessings with its traditional design and exquisite craftsmanship, elevating the sanctity of your pooja altar. Ideal for daily rituals or special occasions, the Shreerang Copper Kalash invites auspiciousness and tradition into your spiritual practices.</div><div><br></div><div>According to Ayurveda, water stored in a copper vessel has the ability to balance all three doshas (vata, kapha, and pitta) by positively charging the water. This multipurpose Kalash is perfect for poojas, home decor, weddings, and other traditional occasions. Made from high-quality copper, it is durable, easy to use, and maintain. Its glossy finish adds to its charm, making it a versatile accessory for all religious festivals and ceremonies.</div>', NULL, 150, 300, NULL, 1, 0, '183.83.147.51', 102, 102, '2024-06-25 10:43:16', '2024-06-25 11:09:18', 'ranged', NULL),
(88, 42, 'Copper Apple Kalash(Apple Gadwa)', '1719313802.jpg', '<div>Shreerang Copper Apple Kalash - Embrace Tradition with Divine Elegance</div><div><br></div><div>Shreerang Copper Apple Kalash is meticulously crafted from pure copper to enhance your festive rituals and daily puja ceremonies. This sacred vessel embodies divine energy and blessings, elevating the sanctity of your pooja altar with its traditional design and exquisite craftsmanship.</div><div><br></div><div>Invite auspiciousness and tradition into your spiritual practices with the Shreerang Copper Kalash. This multipurpose vessel is not only durable and easy to maintain but also enhances the charm of any religious festival or ceremony with its glossy finish. Make it a cherished addition to your puja essentials and experience the divine elegance it brings to your sacred rituals.</div>', NULL, 150, 300, NULL, 1, 0, '183.83.147.51', 102, 102, '2024-06-25 10:53:47', '2024-06-25 11:10:02', 'ranged', NULL),
(89, 42, 'Sugar Pot (Modern Table Top)', '1719486083.jpg', '<div>Our product design team comes up with innovative products after keenly observing the lifestyle of the new age citizen.<span style=\"background-color: var(--vz-card-bg); color: var(--vz-card-color); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--vz-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">The SugarPot(MODERN TABLE TOP) is one such product that lets you harvest the health benefits of Copper, by simply storing &amp; drinking water from it.</span></div><div><span style=\"color: var(--vz-card-color); background-color: var(--vz-card-bg); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--vz-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Be it an Auspicious Event, Decor Or Lifestyle, we have the perfect copper product for every aspect of your life. Find out more at SWASTIK COPPER</span><br></div>', 1100, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '183.83.147.5', 102, 102, '2024-06-27 11:01:23', '2024-07-30 03:57:31', 'fixed', '#swastikcopper #copperbottle #copperproducts #handmade #auspicious #history #metal #pratikcopper #health #wellness #hollistic #wellbeing #healthylifestyle #culture #india #madeinindia #indianhistory #indianculture #wellnessproducts'),
(90, 42, 'Round Sugar Pot', '1719486924.jpg', '<div>Our product design team comes up with innovative products after keenly observing the lifestyle of the new age citizen.<span style=\"background-color: var(--vz-card-bg); color: var(--vz-card-color); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--vz-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">The Round SugarPot&nbsp; is one such product that lets you harvest the health benefits of Copper, by simply storing &amp; drinking water from it.</span></div><div><span style=\"color: var(--vz-card-color); background-color: var(--vz-card-bg); font-family: var(--vz-body-font-family); font-size: var(--vz-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--vz-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--vz-body-text-align);\">Be it an Auspicious Event, Decor Or Lifestyle, we have the perfect copper product for every aspect of your life. Find out more at SWASTIK COPPER</span><br></div>', 1200, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '183.83.146.221', 102, 102, '2024-06-27 11:15:24', '2024-06-27 11:16:05', 'fixed', '#swastikcopper #copperbottle #copperproducts #handmade #auspicious #history #metal #pratikcopper #health #wellness #hollistic #wellbeing #healthylifestyle #culture #india #madeinindia #indianhistory #indianculture #wellnessproducts'),
(91, 45, 'JEWEL OF THE CREEK DUBAI', '1720142876.png', '5Nights 6 Days at just Rs 38000 per person twin sharing .<div><br><div><div>Dubai - the land of the dreams ! Among the top 5 tourist destinations of Asia, Dubai is a blend of modernity and tradition.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Explore Dubai with us. With our customized personal packages enjoy the Dhow Cruises, the Desert Safaris, the world famous iconic Burj Khalifa, the Meena bazaar, spend your time in the ultra luxurious yachts and shop at the 12 million sq ft. Dubai Mall. Flaunt it like Shah Rukh Khan and Kareena Kapoor.</div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>With our customized Dubai packages, leave the planning to us, TraveBee Holidays. And enjoy a momentous vacation with your family, your friends,</div><div><br></div><div>Whether you are seeking a family vacation or a romantic trip, Travebee Holidays has the best Dubai holiday packages to make your trip pocket friendly, stress-free and memorable.&nbsp;</div><div><br></div><div>Connect with us to know the details and make your Holidays beautiful .</div><div><br></div><div>TraveBee Holidays.</div><div><br><div><br></div><div><br><div><br></div></div></div></div></div>', 38000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '42.111.204.12', 105, 105, '2024-07-05 01:27:56', '2024-07-05 01:46:47', 'fixed', '#dubai#uae#abudhabi#Yacht#dubaimall#shopping#travel#travelling#family#tours#vacation#holidays#trip#shorttrip#honeymoon#childfriendly#travebeeholidays'),
(92, 42, 'Table Top', '1720435181.jpg', '<div>Our product design team comes up with innovative products after keenly observing the lifestyle of the new age citizen.</div><div><br></div><div>The TABLE TOP is one such product that lets you harvest the health benefits of Copper, by simply storing &amp; drinking water from it.</div><div><br></div><div>Be it an Auspicious Event, Decor Or Lifestyle, we have the perfect copper product for every aspect of your life. Find out more at SWASTIK COPPER</div>', 1300, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '183.83.147.84', 102, 102, '2024-07-08 10:39:41', '2024-07-08 10:39:54', 'fixed', '#swastikcopper #copperbottle #copperproducts #handmade #auspicious #history #metal #pratikcopper #health #wellness #hollistic #wellbeing #healthylifestyle #culture #india #madeinindia #indianhistory #indianculture #wellnessproducts #tradition #innovation #explorepage');
