(97, 100, 'Clear aligners', '1722081418.jpg', 'Give yourself a chance to carry a perfect smile without any restriction of food or hiding your teeth with clips. It\'s easy to use and very patient friendly alternative for misaligned teeth.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 11:56:58', NULL, NULL, 'Aligners,adult braces,quick makeover, braces, comfortablebraces'),
(98, 100, 'Dental implants', '1722081981.jpg', 'Dental implant is one of the best option for the replacement of missing teeth at any age. It works as well as natural teeth and very comfortable while chewing and speaking.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 12:06:21', NULL, NULL, 'Dentalimplants, Fixed Teeth, naturalsmile, confidentsmile, cosmeticdentistry, dentalcare, oralsurgery, oralhealth, smilemakeover,'),
(99, 100, 'Root canal treatment', '1722082524.jpg', 'Root canal treatment is the most common carried out procedure for grossly damaged teeth due to cavities or some other reason. Due to advancement in equipments and materials, it can be carried out in single appointment as well in some cases without facing any pain.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 12:15:24', NULL, NULL, 'RCT, painfreeRCT, toothsaving, root canal,endodontics, dentistry, rootcanaltreatment, smile, rerootcanal, surgicalendodontics'),
(100, 100, 'Oral cancer diagnosis', '1722082815.jpg', 'Oral cancer is one of the most prevalent in our part of the world. If it is diagnosed at early stages, it can improve the prognosis.&nbsp;', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 12:20:15', NULL, NULL, 'Ulcer,nonhealingulcer,redpatch,whitepatch,lessmouthopening,cancer,smoking,tobacco,oralpathologist,cancerdiagnosis'),
(101, 100, 'Wisdom tooth removal', '1722083660.jpg', 'Wisdom tooth pain is one of the common causes of dental pain. It can be due to number of reasons varying from inadequate space in mouth, ill positioned teeth, cavity, gum problem to lesion associated with it. It can cause pain, difficulty in mouth opening, swelling, fever, difficulty in swallowing and inability to bite, sleep disturbances etc. It can be removed under local anaesthesia without much hassle and in painless way.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 12:34:20', NULL, NULL, 'Extrateeth, wisdomtooth, wisdomtoothsurgery, toothremoval, oralsurgery, painlesssurgery,'),
(102, 100, 'Ceramic fixed teeth', '1722084038.jpg', 'Digitally scanned and fabricated ceramic and metal teeth are one of the most advanced dental technology for replacement of missing teeth and for protection of teeth with root canal treatment. It can be inlay,inlay,overlay,crown, bridge etc.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 12:40:38', NULL, NULL, 'Ceramicteeth, fixedteeth, cosmeticdentistry, missingtoothreplacement, whiteteeth, cap, crown, bridge, naturalteeth, artificialteeth, digitalscanning, notoimpressions, metalteeth, inlay, onlay, metalteeth'),
(103, 100, 'Tooth coloured fillings/ restorations', '1722084366.jpg', 'Tooth coloured fillings are one of the most basic dental procedures which helps avoiding the large problem like root canal treatment by keeping teeth healthy and natural. They can merge seamlessly with adjacent area and look very natural.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 12:46:06', NULL, NULL, 'Toothfilling, whitefilling, nocavity, cosmeticfilling, compositefilling, lightcuredfilling, toothrestoration'),
(104, 100, 'Teeth cleaning/ scaling', '1722084726.jpg', 'Scaling or tooth cleaning should be the norm rather than exception for each and every person. It is the most commonly recommended procedure which helps to keep teeth and gums healthy. Routine cleaning helps avoiding tooth loss. It must be part of your oral hygiene maintenance regimen.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 12:52:06', NULL, NULL, 'Cleanteeth, teethcleaning, scaling, smellfreemouth, healthyteeth, healthygums, routinecleaning, painlesscleaning'),
(105, 100, 'Dentures', '1722084996.jpg', 'Complete Dentures and overdentures are prescribed for patients who have lost all the teeth and want quick and easy fix for chewing. It gives you confident smile and ease of removability. It can be made immediately after removal of teeth as well.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 12:56:36', NULL, NULL, 'Dentures, overdenture, removableteeth, semifixeddentures, fullteethreplacement,'),
(106, 100, 'Braces/orthodontic treatment', '1722085466.jpg', 'Metal, ceramic, self ligation braces, lingual braces are all different types of braces wherein teeth can be placed in an ideal position and helps you smile confidently. It is commonly placed in teen aged boys and girls. It protects your natural teeth by moving your teeth in a controlled manner inside your jaw bones.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 13:04:26', NULL, NULL, 'Braces, orthodontics, straightteeth, crookedteeth, spacedteeth, spacing, misalignedteeth, crowdingofteeth, teenagebraces'),
(107, 100, 'Gum surgery/ Flap surgery', '1722086516.jpg', 'Minor surgical procedure of gums can be carried out in local anaesthesia. It is indicated for patients with moderate to severe gum problem after careful analysis. It is painless and gives result in 2-3 weeks. It helps elongate the life span of a tooth. It can be done by scalpel(blade)/ laser.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 13:21:56', NULL, NULL, 'Gumssurgery, minorsurgery, swollengums, weakgums, bleedinggums, pyorrhoeatreatment, deepcleaning, curettage, flap, flap surgery, gumsinfection, gumrepositioning,'),
(108, 100, 'Semifixed teeth/precision attachment', '1722086814.jpg', 'It is one of the modality for teeth replacement in patients where only few teeth are absent and patient\'s systemic condition doesn\'t not allow any surgical procedure and patient does not want dentures. It is quick, predictable and easy procedure which gives immediate benefits.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 13:26:54', NULL, NULL, 'Immediateteeth, noloosedentures, semifixedteeth, precisionattachment, quickteeth'),
(109, 83, 'Vastu Balancing- Residential', '1722087567.png', 'We specialise in Space balancing through ancient Vastu Science. Our USP is NO structural changes, NO demolition and NO additional expensive products. We do panchtattv(5 Elements) balcing in space through colours, patterns, metal. We also do relocation of Utility and activities as per cycle of creation.', NULL, 24000, 100000, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.164.123', 143, 143, '2024-07-27 13:39:27', '2024-07-27 14:34:05', 'ranged', '#mahavastu #mahavastuacharya #vastu #mahagurukul #mahavastutips #vastuacharya #mahavastutips #vastutips #energy #energybalance #16directions #direction #vastushastra #cycleofcreation #5elements #panchtattva #tattvabalance #ahmedabad #global'),
(110, 83, 'Vastu Balancing- Office/Commercial', '1722088759.png', 'We specialise in Space balancing through ancient Vastu Science. Our USP is NO structural changes, NO demolition and NO additional expensive products. We do panchtattv(5 Elements) balcing in space through colours, patterns, metal. We also do relocation of Utility and activities as per cycle of creation.<br>', NULL, 24000, 100000, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.164.123', 143, NULL, '2024-07-27 13:59:19', NULL, 'ranged', '#mahavastu #mahavastuacharya #vastu #mahagurukul #mahavastutips #vastuacharya #mahavastutips #vastutips #energy #energybalance #16directions #direction #vastushastra #cycleofcreation #5elements #panchtattva #tattvabalance #ahmedabad #global'),
(111, 83, 'Vastu Balncing- Factories', '1722089011.png', 'We specialise in Space balancing through ancient Vastu Science. Our USP is NO structural changes, NO demolition and NO additional expensive products. We do panchtattv(5 Elements) balcing in space through colours, patterns, metal. We also do relocation of Utility and activities as per cycle of creation. We deal with all kind of factory issues like quality improvement, production, quality production, leagal issues, partner disputes, labour issues, high expenditure, growth, machinery failure etc<br>', NULL, 24000, 200000, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.164.123', 143, NULL, '2024-07-27 14:03:31', NULL, 'ranged', '#mahavastu #mahavastuacharya #vastu #mahagurukul #mahavastutips #vastuacharya #mahavastutips #vastutips #energy #energybalance #16directions #direction #vastushastra #cycleofcreation #5elements #panchtattva #tattvabalance #ahmedabad #global'),
(112, 100, 'Teeth whitening/bleaching', '1722089713.jpg', 'Teeth whitening is in office procedure in which teeth are made few to many shades lighter/whiter by the help of whitening agents, which can only be used under dentist supervision and protective barrier for gums. It is one of the commonest dental cosmetic procedure.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.135.29', 160, NULL, '2024-07-27 14:15:13', NULL, NULL, 'Whitenteeth, bleaching, whitening, sparklingsmile, cosmetictreatment, pearlywhite, shinyteeth, beautifulsmile,'),
(113, 83, 'NUmerology- Full 50 pages report', '1722090049.png', 'Every number speaks, and your birthday efines what numbers are speaking loud for you. to know which numbers are favolable or is your name suits your birthday or not or to know how to utilise daily date numbers in a beneficiary way, Numerology helps.&nbsp;', 5000, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '42.105.164.123', 143, NULL, '2024-07-27 14:20:49', NULL, 'fixed', '#positivevibes #namenumbers #numerovastu #luckydates #luckycolors #businessname #luckymobile #numerology #love #lawofattraction #numbers #synchronicity');
