(175, 124, 'Bathsalt', '1733414870.jpg', 'Pure Relaxation with SWA\'s Premium Bath SaltsCrafted with the finest, all-natural ingredients, our calming bath salts combine high-grade halite, magnesium sulfate, and carefully selected essential oils to offer you a truly restorative experience.Each ingredient is chosen for its purity and therapeutic benefits. Halite, known for its rich mineral content, and magnesium sulfate, renowned for its calming properties, come together to soothe both the body and mind.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.134.92', 185, 185, '2024-12-05 16:07:50', '2024-12-05 19:41:03', 'ranged', '#bathsalt\r\n#swaluxuriouswellness\r\n#bathsalts\r\n#stressrelief \r\n#naturalbathsalts\r\n#Magnesiumbath\r\n#CalmingBath\r\n#EssentialOils\r\n#RelaxingBath\r\n#selfcare\r\n#relaxing\r\n#StressRelief\r\n#AromatherapyBath\r\n#mindfulness\r\n#mindfulgifting\r\n#wellness\r\n#wellnessproducts'),
(176, 124, 'Florison- Concrete Candle', '1733428511.jpg', 'SWA\'s Florison candles are truly artisan made as well as eco-conscious in nature.<div><br><div>Container: concrete</div><div>Wax capacity: 200g</div><div>Wax type: soy</div><div>Decor and fragrance- fully customizable.&nbsp;</div><div><div><br></div><div>From the concrete containers designed as per the clients color and finishing preferences, to the candle\'s wick and decor, every bit of the candle is customizable, making it uniquely yours. Thus the Florison collection is ideal for memorable gifting, corporate gifting, wedding return favours, or personal use. Once fully used, get them refilled from us or alternatively, use them as pen stands to enjoy its versatility.&nbsp; &nbsp;<div><br></div><div><br></div></div></div></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '49.14.134.92', 185, NULL, '2024-12-05 19:55:11', NULL, NULL, '#candle #candles #soycandle #soywax #soywaxcandles #corporategifting #concretecandle #fragrancecandles #artisancandles #returngifts #weddingfavour #gift #gifting #personalisation #personalise #customisable #customise #swaluxuriouswellness #puresoy #puresoycandles #puresoycandle #nontoxic #nontoxiccandle #nontoxiccandles #sustainable #sustainablegifting #memorablegifts #giftsforher #giftsforhim'),
