(183, 158, 'Project Management Consultancy Service', '1752216650.jpeg', 'Sharanam Civil Consultancy has been established in Oct 2020, and it has almost 5 years of experience. However, my personal experience spans over 34 years. Before venturing into entrepreneurship, I oversaw the development of more than 1.5 crore sq. ft. of residential, commercial, inferior fit-out and mixed-use projects.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, 0, '117.99.100.149', 219, 219, '2025-07-11 06:50:50', '2025-07-24 09:14:11', 'ranged', '#ProjectManagementConsultancy #PMC #ConstructionManagement #PMCServices #InfrastructureConsulting #ConstructionSupervision #ProjectMonitoring #ConstructionPlanning #SiteManagement #CivilEngineering #QualityAssurance #CostControl #ContractManagement #ProcurementManagement #VendorManagement #ConstructionAudit #RiskManagement #TenderManagement #ConstructionScheduling #ConstructionIndustry #RealEstateProjects #ResidentialPMC #CommercialPMC #IndustrialPMC #interiorPMC'),
