(10, 'Ruchi Chandak', '6353131883', 'ruchichandak01@gmail.com', 'Business', 'Service', 'The Spot Design | hospitality brand information', 52, 'Partnership', 'Ahmedabad', 0, '', 'The Spot Design is a contemporary interior studio focused on creating spaces that feel intentional, refined, and deeply personal. We believe every space has a “spot” - a focal point where design meets emotion - and we build around that essence.\r\n\r\nFrom concept to execution, we blend minimal aesthetics, thoughtful detailing, and functional planning to craft interiors that are elegant, timeless, and effortlessly elevated.\r\n\r\nAt The Spot Design, we don’t just design spaces - we curate experiences.', '2026-02-15 15:42:22', '2026-02-15 15:42:22', 'Working on a side project, skill, or business', 'Conversations are informal and equal', 'I’m building or actively growing something', 'Have meaningful conversations, not just cards', 'To contribute skills and perspectives', 'Shubham Surti'),
(11, 'Merlyn George', '799003690', 'merlyngeorge3173@gmail.com', 'Employee', 'Service', 'GRYD', 115, 'LLP', 'Ahmedabad', 0, '', 'Hwnnsbd', '2026-02-19 10:02:17', '2026-02-19 10:02:17', 'Mostly rest and personal time', 'People openly share what they’re building', 'I’m working professionally and open to collaborations', 'Get new perspectives or ideas', 'To collaborate and grow with like-minded people', 'Shubham Surti'),
(12, 'Pratiti Shah', '9662024010', 'pratitishah.strategy@gmail.com', 'Business', 'Product', 'TSFDC', 53, '', 'Indian, Oman, UAE', 0, '', 'Technology Solutions for Digital Commerce is a premier IT solutions\r\nprovider. The company was established to bring together a full suite of\r\ndigital, technological, and IT-driven services under one unified roof.\r\nWith a commitment to innovation, quality, and value-driven service,\r\nwe aim to empower businesses, government entities, and\r\nentrepreneurs with world-class digital solutions that accelerate growth,\r\nstreamline operations, and elevate customer experience.\r\nTechnology Solutions for Digital Commerce is built on the belief that\r\ntechnology should be simple, reliable, and transformative. We deliver\r\ntailor- made IT systems, digital platforms, and managed services\r\ndesigned to meet the evolving needs of organisations in  India, Oman, UAE and beyond.', '2026-02-19 11:44:26', '2026-02-19 11:44:26', '>A mix of chill and something productive', 'Conversations are informal and equal', 'I’m exploring ideas and testing directions', 'Meet people I can collaborate with', 'To gain exposure and direction', 'Parthiv Patel');
